    • Constructor Detail

      • FieldInfo

        public FieldInfo(String tag,
                 String name,
                 int dataType,
                 String encodedLengthTag,
                 int zone,
                 boolean standard)
        Create a field definition for a field with the given characteristics.
        Parameters:
        tag - Field tag.
        name - Field name.
        dataType - Type of data as defined in Constants TYPE values.
        encodedLengthTag - null if this is not encoded field. Otherwise the tag number of the associated length field.
        zone - indicates if field is a header, body or trailer field. See ZONE constants in FieldInfos.
        standard - true if this is a standard FIX field.

      • FieldInfo

        public FieldInfo(String tag,
                 String name,
                 int dataType,
                 String encodedLengthTag,
                 String lengthTag,
                 int zone,
                 boolean standard,
                 List<String> aliases,
                 String description,
                 String deprecation,
                 List<ValueInfo> values)
        Create a field definition for a field with the given characteristics.
        Parameters:
        tag - Field tag.
        name - Field name.
        dataType - Type of data as defined in Constants TYPE values.
        encodedLengthTag - null if this is not encoded field. Otherwise the tag number of the associated length field.
        lengthTag - null if this field is not raw data. Otherwise the tag number of the associated length field.
        zone - indicates if field is a header, body or trailer field. See ZONE constants in FieldInfos.
        standard - true if this is a standard FIX field.
        aliases - a list of aliases.
        description - description
        deprecation - deprecation
        values - values
